{"tid":1227113,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"膠水樽的各種用法","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T09:22:45.000Z","uid":168818,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40bbb541bde4e379ce73de27738c02b81e3ef622","tid":1227113,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"就咁 平時見身邊好多無用水樽 加上本身幾鍾意廢物利用  <br />\n所以順便集合咗些ideas出嚟俾大家參詳吓 以備不時之需:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1) 水樽擴大照明</span></strong><br />\n日本警視廳災害對策課 教大家停電時，只需在手電筒上放上一個入滿水的透明膠樽，就可以將集中的光線散射開去，照亮周圍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/01212848/page00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F01212848%2Fpage00.jpg&h=fd9472c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2) 水樽熱縮膜</span></strong><br />\n亦可以咁樣加熱做簡單接合、組裝物件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1R4HlTdXD9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1R4HlTdXD9Q&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=dfc94bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1R4HlTdXD9Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3) 水樽膠匙/剷</span></strong><br />\nCut普通膠水樽或牛奶樽來當用具。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6gYR8ZWJNi0/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F6gYR8ZWJNi0%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=b5bf7019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.classes.com.hk/userfiles/image/%E5%BB%A2%E7%89%A9%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.classes.com.hk%2Fuserfiles%2Fimage%2F%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25EF%25BC%2592.png&h=802d4173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">4) 水樽密封蓋</span></strong><br />\n常見嘅方法，方便保存袋裝食物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.sundaymore.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/8646cc47dcadc22805c77de7fe5483bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.sundaymore.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2F8646cc47dcadc22805c77de7fe5483bd.jpg&h=e7bc6d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5) 水樽噴咀</span></strong><br />\n花灑式可節約用水，方便洗手/淋花之類。<br />\n集中式可唧得較遠，就算唔入水都仲有好多用途㗎~<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D8LR7XwU0AAIXNl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD8LR7XwU0AAIXNl.jpg&h=348f635b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ue8A6pT0MFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUe8A6pT0MFk&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=ee5584a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ue8A6pT0MFk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">6) 水樽狗用飲水器</span></strong><br />\n最後唔少得，如果你見到某些狗隻企得耐 或發惡亂吠想打人，可能頸渴。<br />\n整完可以放喺佢地面前， 俾佢地慢慢飲， 解暑~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lnYpmz4Q29o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlnYpmz4Q29o&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=9e90ffd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lnYpmz4Q29o</a><br />\n<br />\n仲可以有好多 例如煙頭熄滅器、紙巾盒呀之類等等...<br />\n相信大家都充滿創意 會諗到其他玩法~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95549346964571d76cc01a5bef612f21caee612c","tid":1227113,"uid":168818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"btw 覺得日本災害對策課個twitter(@MPD_bousai)都ok好睇 有唔少小技巧可以學習以備不時之需。<br />\n<br />\n例如若停電又無蠟燭，利用吞拿魚罐頭嘅油當成燃料，配上咖啡濾紙/廚紙卷成燈芯點火照明，夠照2-3個鐘頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【身近なモノ活用術】<br />\n<img src=\"https://rr.img.naver.jp/mig?src=http%3A%2F%2Fimgcc.naver.jp%2Fkaze%2Fmission%2FUSER%2F20170310%2F21%2F2803021%2F12%2F900x1200x03ea68cffd6d435111dc3e5.jpg%2F300%2F600&amp;twidth=300&amp;theight=0&amp;qlt=80&amp;res_format=jpg&amp;op=r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frr.img.naver.jp%2Fmig%3Fsrc%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fimgcc.naver.jp%252Fkaze%252Fmission%252FUSER%252F20170310%252F21%252F2803021%252F12%252F900x1200x03ea68cffd6d435111dc3e5.jpg%252F300%252F600%26twidth%3D300%26theight%3D0%26qlt%3D80%26res_format%3Djpg%26op%3Dr&h=debd67ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ngu7mjJyyf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNgu7mjJyyf4&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=3648759e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ngu7mjJyyf4</a>"},{"pid":"9180e3b659bab2119cbc594e91982e41dd436b73","tid":1227113,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T22:51:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06a395f884e849d6f62be52d12c6504c8c427e16","tid":1227113,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2cd78c7c59033f199aa33f7304fbe4a770daaf8","tid":1227113,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7217652f50dfe0f62dd93be80456c01d980f7d4d","tid":1227113,"uid":281229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oFqNQKQa3HM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoFqNQKQa3HM&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=b7c96a78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oFqNQKQa3HM</a>"}]}